data.description: Discover the charm of this 4-bed, 2-bath home in a tranquil neighborhood. With 1,630 square feet on a generous 0.5-acre lot, this home exudes a cozy, homey feel. The newer roof adds value, and the oversize master bathroom is a nice touch. While it needs remodeling, envision the potential to create your dream space. Embrace the peaceful surroundings and make this house your own haven.
